23
00:01:23,700 --> 00:01:24,340
All right.

24
00:01:24,660 --> 00:01:25,820
Go give out my order.

25
00:01:26,300 --> 00:01:27,700
His Majesty can stand up.

26
00:01:28,620 --> 00:01:29,220
Yes.

27
00:01:51,660 --> 00:01:53,260
