for so many years.

40
00:02:36,380 --> 00:02:38,740
Today, you made me know

41
00:02:40,020 --> 00:02:40,820
protecting someone

42
00:02:42,620 --> 00:02:44,420
could be a happy thing.

43
00:02:49,620 --> 00:02:53,700
And you should also remember
what you said last night.

44
00:02:55,220 --> 00:02:56,860
I'll walk side by side with you

45
00:02:59,100 --> 00:03:00,540
to get back what you have lost,
Your Majesty.

46
00:03:23,780 --> 00:03:24,420
Mother,

47
00:03:25,300 --> 00:03:26,140
