Consort Huan is grounded
for only 30 days.

86
00:05:53,260 --> 00:05:55,300
To take over all the harem affairs

87
00:05:55,740 --> 00:05:57,100
and make her a mere figurehead,

88
00:05:57,660 --> 00:05:59,580
