89
00:06:05,540 --> 00:06:06,460
I get it.

90
00:06:07,820 --> 00:06:09,340
I will do my best

91
00:06:09,740 --> 00:06:11,340
to take away all her power.

92
00:06:12,380 --> 00:06:13,820
She tortured Qingyan,

93
00:06:14,340 --> 00:06:15,540
bullied me,

94
00:06:15,860 --> 00:06:17,020
and humiliated you.

95
00:06:17,260 --> 00:06:20,700
I'll avenge everything.

96
00:06:28,740 --> 00:06:29,580
You have a long way to go.

97
00:06:30,620 --> 00:06:32,220
I'll always protect you.

98
00:06:40,170 --> 00:06:43,760
