109
00:07:08,380 --> 00:07:09,340
- Please punish me, Your Grace.
- Please punish me, Your Grace.

110
00:07:09,580 --> 00:07:12,140
My maids should be severely punished.

111
00:07:12,540 --> 00:07:14,260
If anything like this happens again,

112
00:07:14,940 --> 00:07:15,900
